bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[u]Key Features[/u]
[ul]
Multi-Output Results: Enter one value (like Fractional Feet/Inches) and instantly see the equivalent in Decimal Feet, Millimeters, Meters, and more.
Robust Error Handling: Sophisticated validation loops ensure that only properly formatted data reaches the calculation engine.
[/ul]

[u]Supported Categories[/u]
[ul]
Distance: Fractional/Decimal Feet & Inches, Metric (mm, cm, m)
Mass: Pounds, Kilograms
Pressure: PSI, Mbar
Flow Rate: Barrels per hour, Cubic Meters per hour
[/ul]

[u]Contributors[/u]
[ul]
